{c_label}Cooldown: {/c}{c_resource}{Cooldown Time}{/c} seconds
Raheir strikes the ground {c_number}3{/c} times, each burst dealing {c_number}{payload:STARTER}{/c} Physical damage and Pulling In enemies. The final burst additionally deals {c_number}[{payload:FINISHER}-{payload:STARTER}]{/c} Physical damage and Stuns enemies for {c_number}[{SF_5}]{/c} |4second;seconds.
